name: Papa's Party Tickets
description:
You can buy tickets for Papa's Party for Friday the 31st of May here!

Papa's Party will be in the stunning Chamber East. It shall be a little bit of a celebration featuring live music, art and over 22kg of free Pick n Mix. There will also be a free popcorn bar and nachos with dips. The night will feature photographs from the talented Gavin McLaughlin, Live acts include Panda Su, Yogi and Colour Coded plus special guests. There will also be a heavily discounted entry to Dukes Corner when you attend this event.
